It is low cost, secure, durable storage service that can be used to store long term data for backup or archival.
Glacier data repository is known as Vault.
Any data that is upload to a glacier vault is known as archive retrieving data from glacier is slow and time consuming and typically take 3-4 hrs.
Once the archive is deleted from vault is took 24 hrs to refresh the inventory updated and check the no of archive it show. 
Archive data can upload via AWS CLI because in GUI doesn't support upload data and display data, use GUI Thrid-Party tools like FastGlacier, CloudBerry for uploading archives.
Each archive data while uploaded then assigned a unique archive id of the time creation through an aws cli.